{"id":317710,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/唯色-藏人悼念遇刺身亡的阿贡仁波切/","date":"2013-10-12T17:17:19Z","modified":"2013-10-12T17:17:19Z","title":"唯色 | 藏人悼念遇刺身亡的阿贡仁波切","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-CyIjyD4r478/UlmAzESA1NI/AAAAAAAAXoo/v7xI78gZuEs/s1600/BWO2XqaCIAEKawf.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-CyIjyD4r478/UlmAzESA1NI/AAAAAAAAXoo/v7xI78gZuEs/s1600/BWO2XqaCIAEKawf.jpg\" height=\"640\" width=\"360\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>了解到，这几天，全藏很多地方沉浸在失去阿贡仁波切的悲痛中，许多寺院、学校在为10月8日于成都遇刺身亡的阿贡仁波切举办祈福法会等哀悼仪式，许多藏人知识分子写了纪念诗文。而且，凡是知道、了解阿贡仁波切的藏人们都根本不相信警方公布的所谓因“经济纠纷”导致刺杀的结论，认为这里面另有隐情。</b></p>\n<p><b>这是青海省玉树藏族自治州囊谦县公雅寺所有僧众，举着写有藏中英三种文字的横幅悼念阿贡仁波切，并在寺院举办祈福法会（拍摄于10月10日）：</b></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GYQjA4XxLfs/Ull4D-PoyeI/AAAAAAAAXmY/KNXtOshPc24/s1600/%E5%9C%A8IMG_1390-1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GYQjA4XxLfs/Ull4D-PoyeI/AAAAAAAAXmY/KNXtOshPc24/s1600/%E5%9C%A8IMG_1390-1.jpg\" height=\"360\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-jz0XZpRKRBY/Ull4pEg-juI/AAAAAAAAXmo/roeShLyl17o/s1600/IMG_1388.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-jz0XZpRKRBY/Ull4pEg-juI/AAAAAAAAXmo/roeShLyl17o/s1600/IMG_1388.JPG\" height=\"354\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UdFaBzkMBY0/Ull4v0U890I/AAAAAAAAXm4/3sXIS7npqGE/s1600/IMG_1355.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UdFaBzkMBY0/Ull4v0U890I/AAAAAAAAXm4/3sXIS7npqGE/s1600/IMG_1355.JPG\" height=\"354\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-h0cXOlyOKJQ/Ull4cXXWi7I/AAAAAAAAXmg/ssr6B1Y4eSI/s1600/IMG_1859.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-h0cXOlyOKJQ/Ull4cXXWi7I/AAAAAAAAXmg/ssr6B1Y4eSI/s1600/IMG_1859.JPG\" height=\"48